'''巴特霍爾路'''（{{lang en|Butt Hole Road}}）是一條位於[[英國|英國]][[南約克郡|南約克郡]]{{link-en|唐卡斯特都會自治市|Metropolitan Borough of Doncaster|唐卡斯特市}}{{link-en|科尼斯伯勒|Conisbrough}}的街道，此街道因為其具有暗示性的名稱而於2009年4月更名為'''射手路'''（Archers Way）。<ref name="mail"/>此街道長約150英尺（47米），北端與A630謝菲爾德道連接<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.proviser.com/regional/towns/doncaster/street_maps/page6.html|title=Map of Doncaster Streets, Street Maps of Doncaster: Street Map of Doncaster Streets|work=Proviser|page=6 of 42|accessdate=2009-09-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101231025119/http://www.proviser.com/regional/towns/doncaster/street_maps/page6.html|archivedate=2010-12-31}}</ref>，南端則與布特布斯克步道和烏鴉步道相交。<ref name="map">{{Google maps |url=http://maps.google.co.uk/maps?f=d&source=s_d&saddr=Butt+Hole+Rd&daddr=Butt+Hole+Rd&geocode=FXQcMAMdxoPt_w%3BFdUdMAMdrYLt_w&hl=en&mra=cc&sll=53.484777,-1.211248&sspn=0.000752,0.002411&ie=UTF8&ll=53.484723,-1.211146&spn=0.001503,0.004823&z=18 |title=Butt Hole Rd to Butt Hole Rd |accessdate=2009-09-05}}</ref>因為此街道很短，所以街道旁只建有四間房屋。<ref name="dj">{{cite news|url=http://www.digitaljournal.com/article/273159|title=What’s in a Name? Ask Residents Living on Butt Hole Road|last=Dubroff|first=M Dee|date=27 May 2009|work=DigitalJournal.com|accessdate=2009-09-06|archive-date=2009-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090901230200/http://www.digitaljournal.com/article/273159|dead-url=no}}</ref>這四間房屋皆位於街道的東邊，其門牌號數分別是1、3、5和7。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.houseprices.co.uk/butt-hole-road-conisbrough-doncaster-dn12/|title=Butt Hole Road Conisbrough Doncaster DN12|work=House Prices|accessdate=2009-09-07|archive-date=2010-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101007112422/http://www.houseprices.co.uk/butt-hole-road-conisbrough-doncaster-dn12|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 名稱 ==
儘管唐卡斯特市議會和當地政府機構都表示他們沒有相關的紀錄<ref name="bbc">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/south_yorkshire/3212005.stm|title=Family made butt of jokes|date=24 October 2003|accessdate=2009-01-24|work=BBC News|archive-date=2009-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090130114445/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/south_yorkshire/3212005.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但是巴特霍爾路的居民卻相信此街道是得名自位於這一帶的公用{{link-en|雨水儲集槽|Rainwater tank|雨水收集池}}（雨水收集池的英文名稱為water butt）。<ref name="nyt"/>此街道的英文本名「butt hole」在[[美国英语|美国英语]]中的意思為「[[肛门|肛门]]」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/butt_hole|title=Butt hole|work=Dictionary.com Unabridged (v 1.1)|publisher=[[Random_House|Random House]]|accessdate=2009-09-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024161718/http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/butt_hole|archivedate=2012-10-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ldoceonline.com/dictionary/butthole|title=Butthole|work=Longman Dictionary of Contemporary English|publisher=[[Pearson_Education|Pearson Education]]|accessdate=2009-09-13|archive-date=2010-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101228061018/http://www.ldoceonline.com/dictionary/butthole|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因此很容易讓人誤解街道名真的是指肛门。

==名稱影響==
[[File:Butt_Hole_Road_tourists.jpg|left]]
巴特霍爾路因其具暗示性的名稱而聞名於英國內外。當此街道的路牌圖片在互聯網上出現後，街道很快就聞名國外。在巴特霍爾路獲得知名度後，當地的[[遊覽車|遊覽車]]便開始經過這裡，並會讓遊客下車拍照。<ref name="dj"/>街道的路牌成為整條街的焦點，因此路牌不斷被[[標誌盜竊|偷去]]。而部份遊客更加會在路牌旁露出臀部拍照。<ref name="bbc"/>  

儘管巴特霍爾路成為了一個受歡迎的旅遊目的地，但有些時候傳遞員和計程車司機卻會以為「巴特霍爾路」是一個惡作劇而拒絕提供服務。<ref name="reuters">{{cite news|url=http://www.dojgov.net/ODDNews.htm|title=What's in a Name? Everything When the Name is Butt|date=24 October 2003|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|accessdate=2009-09-07|format=reprint|archive-date=2009-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090402205343/http://www.dojgov.net/ODDNews.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>街道的居民亦經常收到來自惡作劇者的電話。<ref name="bbc"/>於2004年，一篇關於此街道的[[路透社|路透社]]文章指出住在巴特霍爾路上的一個家庭僅僅因為對街道的名稱感到尷尬，所以搬離價值15萬英鎊的平房。<ref>{{cite book|last=Lake|first=Matt|title=Weird England|url=https://archive.org/details/weirdenglandyour0000lake|publisher=Sterling Publishing|location=New York|year=2007|page=[https://archive.org/details/weirdenglandyour0000lake/page/203 203]|isbn=1-4027-4229-0}}</ref>而另一位巴特霍爾路居民則指出他起初以為住在這條街道上會“很有趣”，但街道名稱所帶來的新鮮感很快就消失了。<ref name="star"/>而此街頭的名稱更加啟發了埃德·赫斯特和羅布·貝利創作一本名為《{{link-en|粗魯的英國|Rude Britain}}》（Rude Britain）的書。<ref name="nyt">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/01/23/world/europe/23crapstone.html|title=No Snickering: That Road Sign Means Something Else|first=Sarah|last=Lyall|accessdate=2009-01-24|date=22 January 2009|work=The New York Times|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202225842/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/01/23/world/europe/23crapstone.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 更名 ==
[[File:Conisbrough_Castle_Doncaster_winter_time.jpg|thumb]]
巴特霍爾路成的居民因為不堪大量遊客來訪，以及惡作劇者的騷擾，遂決定將街道名稱改掉。<ref name="mail"/>規劃師亦允許以一個所有居民都不反對的名稱取代現有名稱。因為唐卡斯特市議會只會在路牌損毀後才免費更換路牌，所以街道的居民們只好籌集300英鎊訂造一個新路牌。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rac.co.uk/know-how/motoring-news/item/2009/05/28/residents-rename-butt-hole-road/ |title=Residents rename Butt Hole Road |date=28 May 2009 |work=RAC News |publisher=RAC plc |accessdate=2009-09-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090726201126/http://www.rac.co.uk/know-how/motoring-news/item/2009/05/28/residents-rename-butt-hole-road/ |archivedate=2009-07-26}}</ref>於2009年4月22日，巴特霍爾路正式更名為射手路（Archers Way）。該名稱是以街道附近興建於12世紀的[[中世紀|中世紀]]古蹟[[科尼斯伯勒堡|科尼斯伯勒城堡]]命名。<ref name="star"/><ref name="mail">{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-1187773/Residents-Butt-Hole-Road-club-change-streets-unfortunate-name.html|title=Residents of 'Butt Hole Road' club together to change street's unfortunate name|date=29 May 2009|work=Daily Mail|accessdate=2009-09-06|archive-date=2009-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090904072433/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-1187773/Residents-Butt-Hole-Road-club-change-streets-unfortunate-name.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在名稱更改後不久，網民便於互聯網發表一份請願書，請求居民把街道名稱改回巴特霍爾路。<ref name="star">{{cite news|url=http://www.thestar.co.uk/news/Residents-club-together-to-finally.5305336.jp|title=Residents club together to finally change embarrassing street name|last=Kessen|first=David|date=27 May 2009|work=The Star|publisher=Yorkshire Post Newspapers|accessdate=2009-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090721031637/https://www.thestar.co.uk/news/Residents-club-together-to-finally.5305336.jp|archive-date=2009-07-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>巴特霍爾路更名一事得到了世界各地媒體的關注，其中包括《[[新西蘭先驅報|新西蘭先驅報]]》<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/opinion/news/article.cfm?c_id=466&objectid=10575089|title=''Sideswipe:'' Butt Hole Road|last=Samways|first=Ana|date=29 May 2009|work=The New Zealand Herald|accessdate=2009-09-06|archive-date=2012-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021055611/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/opinion/news/article.cfm?c_id=466&objectid=10575089|dead-url=no}}</ref>、《[[图片报|图片报]]》<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bild.de/BILD/auto/2009/06/a-loch-strasse-kriegt-neuen-namen/strassenname-lustig.html|title="A***-Loch-Straße" bekommt neuen Namen|date=9 June 2009|work=Bild|language=de|accessdate=2009-09-06|archive-date=2009-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090723185055/http://www.bild.de/BILD/auto/2009/06/a-loch-strasse-kriegt-neuen-namen/strassenname-lustig.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和《[[最新消息报|最新消息报]]》。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hln.be/hln/nl/959/Bizar/article/detail/866461/2009/05/27/Bewoners-Kontgatstraat-veranderen-straatnaam.dhtml|title=Bewoners 'Kontgatstraat' veranderen straatnaam|date=27 May 2009|work=Het Laatste Nieuws|language=nl|accessdate=2009-09-06|archive-date=2009-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090530071944/http://www.hln.be/hln/nl/959/Bizar/article/detail/866461/2009/05/27/Bewoners-Kontgatstraat-veranderen-straatnaam.dhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>
